{
  "texts": [
    "Jobs can only require operations that are offered by the assembly system.",
    "A new scheduling decision is requested each time an operation of a job finishes, and the job needs further operations to be implemented.",
    "If a job cannot be assigned to the next station, it blocks the current station until a new assignment can be found.",
    "The transportation time between the current and the following station is calculated on the airline distance using a deterministic transportation velocity.",
    "Stations consist of an input buffer, an output buffer, and mobile resources."
  ]
}